{"tid":535010,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"論唱功，感情，音準，咬字，口音，小肥真係幾好","createTime":"2018-01-20T11:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T04:55:04.000Z","uid":1779,"like":116,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"b2e31f7dec93aef191ec13680745b7b5ec9c9be4","tid":535010,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/opy7OTXjg7Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fopy7OTXjg7Y&d=E75aot0gCfojnsAZZOEX8xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=f881e7ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/opy7OTXjg7Y</a><br />\n同車丸丸唱既經典 老老實實唱第一句都毛管棟 <br />\n口音唱出來順耳 尾音有佢獨特之處 聲音辨識度極高<br />\n睇得出佢雖然唔係唱得輕鬆 但聽落係非常舒服<br />\n大把香港男歌手唱live個pitch唔夠準 一路聽一路驚佢走音<br />\n聽小肥就好淡定 唔會驚佢飄pitch<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MpfEdr9dzQk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMpfEdr9dzQk&d=E75aot0gCfojnsAZZOEX8xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=463ff54a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MpfEdr9dzQk</a><br />\n前排個個share讚好既 唱返自己首本名曲 <br />\n基本上冇人唱得好過佢(其實冇乜歌手翻唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n首詞就唔評論 但隻歌本身都難唱 真假音係咁換 音準要準之餘仲要夠氣 依點一聽live就見真章<br />\n<br />\n以現今樂壇來講，綜合各種歌唱技巧，我覺得小肥真係top<br />\n人氣強如柏宇 live都係差d 雖然大致上都ok<br />\n比比鳥 坤狗 仲有d阿豬阿狗就更加得啖笑"},{"pid":"74580874b02ba9d65189be6e706df9fd550384ed","tid":535010,"uid":1779,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"真心唔明小肥咁都彈唔起<br />\n真係因爲個樣唔夠偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n想當年寵物一出 個個同學仔都識唱囇全首"},{"pid":"a8d50ac8e3663f087fea894ac0e11dd56bd18abe","tid":535010,"uid":134474,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:56:21.000Z","msg":"一直覺得小肥好有實力，唔知點解就係彈唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d9201fc1147a3a99b535798383d5c109ad5746","tid":535010,"uid":1779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T11:56:22.000